description:
This week we share our thoughts on Ghostbusters Frozen Empire, the ongoing war between games journalists and normal people who just want entertainment, and rumours that The Acolyte has already been cancelled before it even releases. Join me, MauLer, GeorgeTheGiantSlayer, Geeks+Gamers and Endymion at the bar!

Subscribe to George: https://www.youtube.com/@GeorgeTheGiantSlayer
Subscribe to Geeks+Gamers: https://www.youtube.com/@GeeksandGamers
Subscribe to Endymiontv: https://www.youtube.com/@EndymionTv
title: Open Bar #89 - Ghostbusters Frozen Empire, The War For Gaming, Acolyte Season 2 Cancelled?
